1
00:00:07,400 --> 00:00:11,460
♪Just To Meet You, you fell for me♪

2
00:00:11,480 --> 00:00:15,460
♪Just to meet me, into my trap you fell♪

3
00:00:15,460 --> 00:00:19,240
♪Wanna try a breathless love?♪

4
00:00:19,240 --> 00:00:23,490
♪Every move hits the heart, close and sure♪

5
00:00:23,490 --> 00:00:27,460
♪Just To Meet You, you love my playful charm♪

6
00:00:27,460 --> 00:00:31,480
♪Just to meet me,
my romantic little schemes for you♪

7
00:00:31,480 --> 00:00:35,170
♪Wanna play another brand-new game?♪

8
00:00:35,170 --> 00:00:40,360
♪Layer by layer, we close the gap♪

9
00:00:40,380 --> 00:00:47,140
=Just To Meet You=

10
00:01:05,100 --> 00:01:07,540
=Episode 5=
=I'll Never Fall in Love with You Again=

11
00:01:23,300 --> 00:01:24,300
(Li Group)

12
00:01:24,300 --> 00:01:25,460
(Password)

13
00:01:31,760 --> 00:01:34,120
Looks like I underestimated their firewall.

14
00:01:37,100 --> 00:01:38,140
(Logging in)

15
00:01:38,140 --> 00:01:39,940
(Li's Group's Internal Information System)

16
00:01:43,100 --> 00:01:43,980
(Patient Database)

17
00:01:43,990 --> 00:01:46,480
(Li Group has all patient data in Manlong.)

18
00:01:46,480 --> 00:01:47,360
(This time,)

19
00:01:47,360 --> 00:01:48,680
(Age Gender Male)
(I can find Xiaodi.)

20
00:01:51,120 --> 00:01:51,960
(Not this one.)

21
00:01:52,200 --> 00:01:53,040
(Not this either.)

22
00:01:53,640 --> 00:01:55,350
(None of these match Xiaodi's info.)

23
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:57,680
(Xiaodi.)

24
00:01:58,120 --> 00:01:59,280
(Where on earth are you?)

25
00:02:02,900 --> 00:02:04,060
(A Total of 153 Candidates
Have Been Selected for You)

26
00:02:10,540 --> 00:02:11,380
(003 Health Examination Form)

27
00:02:11,380 --> 00:02:12,710
Blood type O.

28
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:14,520
RH negative.

29
00:02:14,630 --> 00:02:17,360
Bone marrow DRB1*01:01.

30
00:02:19,520 --> 00:02:20,360
What a pity.

31
00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:22,120
Just another rare blood type patient

32
00:02:22,520 --> 00:02:24,870
who needs a bone marrow transplant
like Xiaodi.

33
00:02:59,240 --> 00:03:00,960
You're trying to leave me again?

34
00:03:07,910 --> 00:03:08,840
Why would I?

35
00:03:09,710 --> 00:03:10,590
I told you

36
00:03:10,910 --> 00:03:12,960
I wouldn't leave you this time.

37
00:03:15,470 --> 00:03:17,310
(After all, only your family)

38
00:03:17,310 --> 00:03:18,800
(can help me find Xiaodi.)

39
00:03:19,910 --> 00:03:20,840
Really?

40
00:03:29,040 --> 00:03:33,110
♪You pull me under,
like a fire burning inside me♪

41
00:03:33,350 --> 00:03:37,200
♪Beneath the black gown,
reborn as a prisoner♪

42
00:03:37,200 --> 00:03:39,090
♪Your love, your rules♪

43
00:03:39,090 --> 00:03:42,390
♪As the world falls, only you stay whole♪

44
00:03:42,390 --> 00:03:46,600
♪Bound in life and death,
mad as doom gamblers♪

45
00:03:48,280 --> 00:03:49,840
Remember what you said.

46
00:03:50,710 --> 00:03:52,310
Even death won't make you leave me.

47
00:03:54,590 --> 00:03:55,560
(Jiang Niannian.)

48
00:03:56,080 --> 00:03:56,960
(This life,)

49
00:03:57,590 --> 00:03:59,350
(I won't repeat the same mistake.)

50
00:04:03,070 --> 00:04:07,330
♪You pull me under,
like a fire burning inside me♪

51
00:04:07,390 --> 00:04:11,280
♪Beneath the black gown,
reborn as a prisoner♪

52
00:04:11,280 --> 00:04:13,180
♪Your love, your rules♪

53
00:04:13,180 --> 00:04:16,400
♪As the world falls, only you stay whole♪

54
00:04:16,400 --> 00:04:20,580
♪Bound in life and death,
mad as doom gamblers♪

55
00:04:37,310 --> 00:04:39,000
Where's Ye Lang?

56
00:04:42,390 --> 00:04:43,230
Come in.

57
00:04:45,750 --> 00:04:46,590
Ms. Jiang.

58
00:04:46,940 --> 00:04:49,040
Ma'am asked you to change and have breakfast.

59
00:04:58,750 --> 00:05:00,240
(It seems in this family,)

60
00:05:00,240 --> 00:05:02,040
(not a single day is peaceful.)

61
00:05:09,190 --> 00:05:11,830
(What an extravagant house.)

62
00:05:19,120 --> 00:05:19,960
Ms. Jiang,

63
00:05:21,120 --> 00:05:22,310
your outfit today

64
00:05:22,600 --> 00:05:24,070
really suits your nature,

65
00:05:24,630 --> 00:05:26,190
using your looks to get what you want.

66
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:31,510
Wasn't it Mrs. Liu who asked me to wear it?

67
00:05:32,310 --> 00:05:33,430
I thought

68
00:05:34,190 --> 00:05:35,390
Mrs. Liu wanted to show me

69
00:05:35,390 --> 00:05:37,600
the Li family's standards.

70
00:05:45,720 --> 00:05:47,830
That's for Ms. Murong Xue.

71
00:05:50,310 --> 00:05:52,000
That's for the Second Young Master.

72
00:05:53,360 --> 00:05:54,430
Then where do I sit?

73
00:05:56,870 --> 00:05:58,070
Ms. Jiang,

74
00:05:58,390 --> 00:05:59,230
you

75
00:05:59,480 --> 00:06:01,160
grew up in a rough neighborhood,

76
00:06:02,120 --> 00:06:03,480
so of course you don't understand

77
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:05,830
everyone has their proper place.

78
00:06:06,310 --> 00:06:08,310
If you can't find yours,

79
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:10,870
then go back to where you came from.

80
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:13,830
Unless...

81
00:06:18,870 --> 00:06:20,310
When Master gets here,

82
00:06:21,560 --> 00:06:23,560
you serve him breakfast.

83
00:06:26,190 --> 00:06:27,950
As long as Master accepts you,

84
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:30,240
then you'll naturally earn a seat

85
00:06:30,240 --> 00:06:31,870
at the Li family table.

86
00:06:32,630 --> 00:06:33,950
(A woman must know when to yield.)

87
00:06:34,360 --> 00:06:35,240
(For Xiaodi,)

88
00:06:35,240 --> 00:06:36,080
(I can put up with anything.)

89
00:06:36,430 --> 00:06:37,870
(It's just a bowl of porridge.)

90
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:41,440
It's so hot.

91
00:06:41,920 --> 00:06:42,760
Wait.

92
00:06:43,600 --> 00:06:44,870
In our family,

93
00:06:45,190 --> 00:06:47,430
when you serve elders porridge,

94
00:06:47,800 --> 00:06:49,640
you can't put it down

95
00:06:49,950 --> 00:06:51,830
without their permission.

96
00:06:54,000 --> 00:06:54,840
So...

97
00:06:55,310 --> 00:06:56,160
Ms. Jiang,

98
00:06:56,470 --> 00:06:57,470
are you

99
00:06:57,560 --> 00:06:59,310
giving up on joining us?

100
00:07:00,310 --> 00:07:02,240
(As if I care about joining your family.)

101
00:07:02,870 --> 00:07:04,630
(There's no one human here,)

102
00:07:04,630 --> 00:07:05,640
(all monsters.)

103
00:07:05,640 --> 00:07:06,940
(Maiden Liu, Servant of the Li Family)

104
00:07:07,720 --> 00:07:09,390
Just wait here.

105
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:12,510
(How has Ye Lang lived all these years?)

106
00:07:12,870 --> 00:07:14,240
(If not for finding my brother,)

107
00:07:14,240 --> 00:07:15,680
(I would never tolerate this.)

108
00:07:54,750 --> 00:07:56,720
(As expected of the top family in Manlong.)

109
00:07:57,120 --> 00:08:00,240
(My first three husbands
had no such manners.)

110
00:08:15,310 --> 00:08:16,150
Master.

111
00:08:16,630 --> 00:08:18,040
For this morning's porridge,

112
00:08:18,480 --> 00:08:19,430
I had the kitchen prepare broth

113
00:08:19,560 --> 00:08:21,360
from century-old turtle shell.

114
00:08:21,510 --> 00:08:22,600
A few days ago,

115
00:08:22,750 --> 00:08:23,750
we received

116
00:08:23,750 --> 00:08:25,070
glutinous rice from Myanmar,

117
00:08:25,430 --> 00:08:27,430
so we made it with blood bird's nest.

118
00:08:28,120 --> 00:08:29,510
To accompany it,

119
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:31,390
we have white caviar,

120
00:08:32,200 --> 00:08:33,320
light and fresh,

121
00:08:33,320 --> 00:08:34,200
very nourishing.

122
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:35,120
Just perfect.

123
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:36,560
Mm.

124
00:08:37,720 --> 00:08:38,960
(This porridge)

125
00:08:39,150 --> 00:08:41,120
(could cover Xiaodi's
hospital bills for years.)

126
00:08:43,030 --> 00:08:44,000
No manners.

127
00:08:44,510 --> 00:08:45,910
When serving the master,

128
00:08:45,910 --> 00:08:46,750
you must kneel.

129
00:09:06,440 --> 00:09:07,280
It's this outfit.

130
00:09:07,750 --> 00:09:08,590
What are you doing?

131
00:09:09,600 --> 00:09:10,750
Are you trying to burn Master?

132
00:09:11,150 --> 00:09:12,390
Hurry, clean this up.

133
00:09:12,390 --> 00:09:13,240
Come here.

134
00:09:13,320 --> 00:09:14,510
Why is she here?

135
00:09:16,510 --> 00:09:17,600
I'm sorry, Master.

136
00:09:17,960 --> 00:09:19,120
It's all my fault.

137
00:09:19,870 --> 00:09:20,790
I just thought

138
00:09:21,080 --> 00:09:23,750
Young Master values Ms. Jiang,

139
00:09:24,240 --> 00:09:27,030
so I had her serve your breakfast.

140
00:09:27,550 --> 00:09:28,600
We're all family.

141
00:09:28,750 --> 00:09:29,590
Get out.

142
00:09:32,720 --> 00:09:34,360
Then I'll come serve you tomorrow.

143
00:09:51,870 --> 00:09:54,440
This ointment works great on burns.

144
00:09:55,440 --> 00:09:56,720
Thank you, Ms. Murong.

145
00:09:57,910 --> 00:09:58,750
By the way,

146
00:09:59,120 --> 00:10:00,390
do you know which hospital

147
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:03,030
in Manlong has the best neurosurgeon?

148
00:10:04,670 --> 00:10:05,750
You should ask Lang.

149
00:10:06,320 --> 00:10:08,510
He knows top medical experts

150
00:10:08,670 --> 00:10:09,790
across the country.

151
00:10:12,320 --> 00:10:14,120
I didn't see him this morning.

152
00:10:15,390 --> 00:10:17,150
He didn't come to breakfast either.

153
00:10:17,670 --> 00:10:18,870
Didn't he tell you?

154
00:10:19,080 --> 00:10:20,600
He went to the office early

155
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:22,390
to prepare for tonight's auction banquet.

156
00:10:23,200 --> 00:10:24,120
Auction banquet?

157
00:10:24,270 --> 00:10:25,150
Mm.

158
00:10:25,270 --> 00:10:26,720
An auction hosted by the Li family.

159
00:10:27,630 --> 00:10:29,600
All of Manlong's elite,

160
00:10:29,600 --> 00:10:30,790
wealthy families,

161
00:10:31,120 --> 00:10:32,670
and medical industry leaders

162
00:10:33,120 --> 00:10:34,000
will be there.

163
00:10:34,870 --> 00:10:35,790
I heard a spot

164
00:10:35,790 --> 00:10:36,960
was specially reserved for you.

165
00:10:37,840 --> 00:10:39,550
You must dress up beautifully tonight.

166
00:10:40,790 --> 00:10:41,630
Got it.

167
00:10:41,870 --> 00:10:43,000
Thanks, Ms. Murong.

168
00:10:44,080 --> 00:10:45,200
It doesn't hurt anymore.

169
00:10:49,480 --> 00:10:50,840
The leading lady is in place.

170
00:10:51,790 --> 00:10:52,630
Tonight,

171
00:10:54,240 --> 00:10:55,750
there'll be a good show.

172
00:11:00,600 --> 00:11:01,440
Miss,

173
00:11:01,670 --> 00:11:02,750
your invitation, please.

174
00:11:02,960 --> 00:11:05,480
Ye Lang invited me.

175
00:11:05,790 --> 00:11:06,630
I'm his wife,

176
00:11:06,790 --> 00:11:07,630
Jiang Niannian.

177
00:11:07,840 --> 00:11:08,840
So you're Ms. Jiang.

178
00:11:09,360 --> 00:11:11,550
I see your name on the guest list.

179
00:11:12,790 --> 00:11:14,270
So can I go in now?

180
00:11:14,630 --> 00:11:15,470
Of course.

181
00:11:15,600 --> 00:11:17,440
But not through this entrance.

182
00:11:17,910 --> 00:11:19,080
Not here.

183
00:11:19,080 --> 00:11:19,960
Then where?

184
00:11:20,080 --> 00:11:21,960
This is the guest entrance.

185
00:11:22,510 --> 00:11:23,720
Aren't I a guest?

186
00:11:23,910 --> 00:11:25,480
Ms. Jiang, you must be mistaken.

187
00:11:25,670 --> 00:11:26,630
You're not a guest.

188
00:11:27,030 --> 00:11:27,870
You're the auction item.

189
00:11:30,270 --> 00:11:31,840
(It's a trap.)

190
00:11:32,630 --> 00:11:34,200
I think you've got it wrong.

191
00:11:58,000 --> 00:11:59,270
Ladies and gentlemen,

192
00:11:59,600 --> 00:12:00,960
tonight's final item

193
00:12:00,960 --> 00:12:02,000
is an absolute rarity.

194
00:12:02,000 --> 00:12:03,270
Spend one night with her,

195
00:12:03,390 --> 00:12:04,590
and you'll have no regrets.

196
00:12:04,720 --> 00:12:05,560
Starting bid,

197
00:12:05,870 --> 00:12:06,710
30 million.

198
00:12:06,960 --> 00:12:09,200
Who'll be tonight's lucky one?

199
00:12:10,840 --> 00:12:12,600
(Stay calm now that I'm here.)

200
00:12:12,840 --> 00:12:15,080
(I'll find a way out later.)

201
00:12:17,200 --> 00:12:18,040
40 million!

202
00:12:18,390 --> 00:12:19,270
40 million.

203
00:12:19,510 --> 00:12:20,750
Any higher?

204
00:12:20,750 --> 00:12:21,870
45 million.

205
00:12:22,030 --> 00:12:23,480
45 million!

206
00:12:23,960 --> 00:12:24,960
Nobody outbid me.

207
00:12:25,150 --> 00:12:26,840
50 million, she's mine.

208
00:12:26,910 --> 00:12:27,750
The beauty's looking at me.

209
00:12:27,870 --> 00:12:28,710
She's coming with me.

210
00:12:28,720 --> 00:12:29,560
I bid 80 million.

211
00:12:29,870 --> 00:12:30,750
80 million!

212
00:12:31,440 --> 00:12:34,080
Top bid is now 80 million.

213
00:12:34,630 --> 00:12:36,720
(Let's see who set this up.)

214
00:12:38,390 --> 00:12:39,270
(Jiang Niannian.)

215
00:12:39,630 --> 00:12:41,360
(Know your place.)

216
00:12:42,120 --> 00:12:44,550
(You're just an auction showpiece.)

217
00:12:45,360 --> 00:12:46,510
(And I)

218
00:12:46,510 --> 00:12:49,670
(am the one who stands beside Ye Lang.)

219
00:12:49,670 --> 00:12:51,300
(Jiang Qingqing, Jiang Niannian's Stepsister)

220
00:12:53,480 --> 00:12:54,840
(Why her?)

221
00:12:54,840 --> 00:12:56,150
(Jiang Qingqing.)

222
00:13:15,080 --> 00:13:21,670
♪Stitched-up lips
tear open a blood-red dusk♪

223
00:13:23,480 --> 00:13:29,690
♪You return reborn,
seeing through all my cracks♪

224
00:13:30,240 --> 00:13:37,240
♪This tenderness, a trap or a gift?♪

225
00:13:37,990 --> 00:13:40,460
♪Still, I'd wager my next life on it♪

226
00:13:40,460 --> 00:13:45,460
♪Just for a moment to recognize you again♪

227
00:13:45,460 --> 00:13:49,690
♪You are the blazing light in my despair♪

228
00:13:50,200 --> 00:13:54,130
♪Lighting the edges of my frozen wings♪

229
00:13:54,180 --> 00:13:57,970
♪I burn myself,
leaping into an illusion of fire♪

230
00:13:57,970 --> 00:14:03,720
♪Breaking free
from dead vines in the ashes♪

231
00:14:03,720 --> 00:14:08,040
♪You are the brightest star in the night♪

232
00:14:08,080 --> 00:14:11,900
♪Awakening my dormant fate♪

233
00:14:11,910 --> 00:14:16,400
♪Freeing me from this half-life prison♪

234
00:14:16,430 --> 00:14:21,260
♪As the bells shatter the past♪

235
00:14:21,660 --> 00:14:28,200
♪Life finds its way again♪

